        <td>
          <para styleclass="Body Text">The <text styleclass="VariableName">Front-View</text> of the <text styleclass="VariableName-IT" style="color:#ff0000;">new</text>&#32;<text styleclass="Interface">Mechanism-Editor</text>:</para>
